---
title: Hearty Vegetable Shepherd's Pie with Chive Potatoes
description: The combination of onion, carrot and celery is called 'mirepoix' in French cooking. It is a classic trio of ingredients used as the flavour base for many recipes. We've harnessed this great technique to help add heartiness to our veggie twist on a classic comfort meal.
